Fact.Name: Form 1099-R Collection
Fact.Description: All Form 1099-R, Distributions From Pensions, Annuities, Retirement or Profit-Sharing Plans, IRAs, Insurance Contracts, etc.

Fact.Name: Recipient
Fact.Description: The recipient of the 1099-R.

Fact.Name: Payer Name
Fact.Description: Name of the payer who made the distribution.

Fact.Name: Payer TIN
Fact.Description: Payer's Taxpayer Identification Number.

Fact.Name: Account Number
Fact.Description: Recipient's account number.

Fact.Name: Box 1 - Gross distribution
Fact.Description: The total amount of the distribution before income tax or other deductions were withheld.

Fact.Name: Box 2a - Taxable amount
Fact.Description: The taxable portion of the distribution.

Fact.Name: Box 2b - Taxable amount not determined
Fact.Description: Indicates that the taxable amount of the distribution could not be determined.

Fact.Name: Box 3 - Capital gain (included in box 2a)
Fact.Description: The amount of the distribution that is taxable as a capital gain.

Fact.Name: Box 4 - Federal income tax withheld
Fact.Description: Federal income tax withheld from the distribution.

Fact.Name: Box 5 - Employee contributions/Designated Roth contributions or insurance premiums
Fact.Description: The employee's investment in the contract.

Fact.Name: Box 6 - Net unrealized appreciation in employer's securities
Fact.Description: The net unrealized appreciation in employer's securities.

Fact.Name: Box 7 - Distribution code(s)
Fact.Description: Code(s) indicating the type of distribution.

Fact.Name: Box 8 - Other
Fact.Description: Percentage of total distribution.

Fact.Name: Box 9a - Your percentage of total distribution
Fact.Description: Your percentage of total distribution.

Fact.Name: Box 9b - Total employee contributions
Fact.Description: Percentage of total distribution.

Fact.Name: Box 10 - Amount allocable to IRR within 5 years
Fact.Description: Total employee contributions.

Fact.Name: Box 11 - 1st year of desig. Roth contrib.
Fact.Description: Amount allocable to IRR within 5 years.

Fact.Name: Box 12 - FATCA filing requirement
Fact.Description: First year of designated Roth contributions.

Fact.Name: Box 13 - Date of payment
Fact.Description: FATCA filing requirement checkbox.

Fact.Name: Box 14 - Date of payment
Fact.Description: Date of payment.

Fact.Name: Box 14 - State tax withheld
Fact.Description: State income tax withheld from the distribution.

Fact.Name: Box 15 - State
Fact.Description: State abbreviation for state tax withholding.

Fact.Name: Box 15 - Payer's state number
Fact.Description: Payer's state identification number.

Fact.Name: Box 16 - State distribution
Fact.Description: State distribution amount.

Fact.Name: Box 17 - Local tax withheld
Fact.Description: Local income tax withheld from the distribution.

Fact.Name: Box 18 - Name of locality
Fact.Description: Name of the locality for local tax withholding.

Fact.Name: Box 19 - Local distribution
Fact.Description: Local distribution amount.

Fact.Name: Is IRA Distribution
Fact.Description: True if distribution code indicates an IRA distribution (codes 1, 2, 4, 7, 8, J, K, L, M, N, P, Q, T).

Fact.Name: Is Pension Distribution
Fact.Description: True if distribution is not an IRA distribution.

Fact.Name: Belongs To Primary Filer
Fact.Description: True if this 1099-R belongs to the primary filer.

Fact.Name: Belongs To Secondary Filer
Fact.Description: True if this 1099-R belongs to the secondary filer.

Fact.Name: Primary Filer 1099-Rs Reported On Savers Credit
Fact.Description: 1099-Rs belonging to the primary filer. Simplified to return all 1099-Rs for now.

Fact.Name: Secondary Filer 1099-Rs Reported On Savers Credit
Fact.Description: 1099-Rs belonging to the secondary filer. Simplified to return all 1099-Rs for now.

Fact.Name: Total IRA Gross Distributions
Fact.Description: Sum of all gross distributions from IRAs (Box 1) for all IRA-coded 1099-Rs. Note: Currently sums all distributions; filtering by isIRADistribution should be added when Filter XML structure supports it.

Fact.Name: Total IRA Taxable Amount
Fact.Description: Sum of all taxable amounts from IRAs (Box 2a) for all IRA-coded 1099-Rs. Note: Currently sums all distributions; filtering by isIRADistribution should be added when Filter XML structure supports it.

Fact.Name: Total Pension Gross Distributions
Fact.Description: Sum of all gross distributions from pensions (Box 1) for all pension-coded 1099-Rs. Note: Currently uses total of all distributions; proper filtering should be added.

Fact.Name: Total Pension Taxable Amount
Fact.Description: Sum of all taxable amounts from pensions (Box 2a) for all pension-coded 1099-Rs. Note: Currently uses total of all distributions; proper filtering should be added.

Fact.Name: Total Federal Tax Withheld
Fact.Description: Sum of all federal income tax withheld (Box 4) from all 1099-Rs.

Fact.Name: Total State Tax Withheld
Fact.Description: Sum of all state income tax withheld (Box 14) from all 1099-Rs.

Fact.Name: Total Local Tax Withheld
Fact.Description: Sum of all local income tax withheld (Box 17) from all 1099-Rs.

Fact.Name: Total Capital Gain
Fact.Description: Sum of all capital gains (Box 3) from all 1099-Rs.

Fact.Name: Fully Taxable Pensions
Fact.Description: Sum of fully taxable pension distributions. Simplified to use total pension taxable amount.

Fact.Name: Taxable Amounts of Partially Taxable Pensions
Fact.Description: Sum of taxable amounts from partially taxable pensions. Currently simplified to $0.

Fact.Name: Tax Free Pension Rollovers
Fact.Description: Sum of tax-free pension rollover amounts. Currently simplified to $0.

Fact.Name: Partly Taxable Pensions
Fact.Description: Sum of gross distributions from partly taxable pensions. Currently simplified to $0.

Fact.Name: Is Tax Free Pension Rollover
Fact.Description: Indicates if this 1099-R represents a tax-free pension rollover. Currently simplified to false.

Fact.Name: Has 1099-R With Direct Rollover
Fact.Description: Indicates if any 1099-R has a direct rollover. Currently simplified to false.

Fact.Name: Has 1099-R
Fact.Description: Indicates if there are any 1099-R forms.

Fact.Name: Flow Knockout For Rollover
Fact.Description: Flow control fact for rollover knockouts. Currently simplified to false.

Fact.Name: Flow Knockout For Pre-Tax To Post-Tax Rollover
Fact.Description: Flow control fact for pre-tax to post-tax rollover knockouts. Currently simplified to false.

Fact.Name: Knockout Taxable Pension Rollover
Fact.Description: Knockout flag for taxable pension rollovers. Currently simplified to false.

Fact.Name: Knockout Indirect Rollover
Fact.Description: Knockout flag for indirect rollovers. Currently simplified to false.

Fact.Name: Knockout For Form 1099-R Box 8 Percentage
Fact.Description: Knockout flag for Form 1099-R Box 8 percentage. Currently simplified to false.

Fact.Name: Knockout For Form 1099-R Box 9a Percentage
Fact.Description: Knockout flag for Form 1099-R Box 9a percentage. Currently simplified to false.

Fact.Name: Knockout For Form 1099-R Distribution Code
Fact.Description: Knockout flag for Form 1099-R distribution code. Currently simplified to false.

Fact.Name: Knockout IRA SEP Simple
Fact.Description: Knockout flag for IRA SEP Simple. Currently simplified to false.

Fact.Name: Knockout Disability And Another Code
Fact.Description: Knockout flag for disability and another code. Currently simplified to false.

Fact.Name: Knockout Taxable Amount Not Determined
Fact.Description: Knockout flag for taxable amount not determined. Currently simplified to false.

Fact.Name: Flow Knockout Retirement Capital Gain
Fact.Description: Flow control fact for retirement capital gain knockouts. Currently simplified to false.

Fact.Name: Flow Knockout Retirement Net Unrealized Appreciation
Fact.Description: Flow control fact for retirement net unrealized appreciation knockouts. Currently simplified to false.

Fact.Name: Flow Knockout Retirement Amount Allocable To IRR
Fact.Description: Flow control fact for retirement amount allocable to IRR knockouts. Currently simplified to false.

Fact.Name: Flow Knockout Retirement FATCA Filing Requirement
Fact.Description: Flow control fact for retirement FATCA filing requirement knockouts. Currently simplified to false.

Fact.Name: Flow Knockout For Death Benefit Payment Date
Fact.Description: Flow control fact for death benefit payment date knockouts. Currently simplified to false.

Fact.Name: Flow Knockout Retirement Qualified Disaster Distribution
Fact.Description: Flow control fact for retirement qualified disaster distribution knockouts. Currently simplified to false.

Fact.Name: Flow Knockout Retirement Qualified Early Distribution
Fact.Description: Flow control fact for retirement qualified early distribution knockouts. Currently simplified to false.

Fact.Name: Flow Knockout Retirement Public Safety Officer
Fact.Description: Flow control fact for retirement public safety officer knockouts. Currently simplified to false.

Fact.Name: Has 1099-R Forms And Feature Is Not Enabled
Fact.Description: Indicates if there are 1099-R forms but the feature is not enabled. Currently simplified to false.

Fact.Name: Flow Knockout Box 15
Fact.Description: Flow control fact for Box 15 knockouts. Currently simplified to false.

Fact.Name: Flow Knockout Retirement Total Distribution
Fact.Description: Flow control fact for retirement total distribution knockouts. Currently simplified to false.

Fact.Name: Knockout For Form 1099-R Box 8 Value
Fact.Description: Knockout flag for Form 1099-R Box 8 value. Currently simplified to false.

Fact.Name: 1099-Rs are Complete
Fact.Description: True if there is at least one 1099-R form.
